            <title>[LU-14504] default LMV delete trigger asstion in osp_xattr_del()</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-14504</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;In lod_declare_xattr_del(), if object doesn&apos;t exist, it&apos;s skipped, but in lod_xattr_del_internal(), it doesn&apos;t check existence, which will trigger assertion in osp_xattr_del().&lt;/p&gt;</description>
